{"word":"ραφή","slug":"ραφή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ραφή</b></el> <el>(ρᾰφή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ράπτω'><el>ράπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a seam</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>sutura</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>the suture</i> of the skull, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; so, <el>ραφαὶ ὀστέων</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}